TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION transformation performs a lookup on target table, DAY_DIMENSION
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_DAY_DIMENSION1

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT min(DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE) AS AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY AS CY_YEAR_YYYY, min(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_MONTH_NUM) AS CY_MONTH_NUM, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0') AS CY_WK_OF_YEAR, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0') AS FISCAL_YR_WK_ID FROM DAY_DIMENSION GROUP BY DAY_DIMENSION.AS_OF_DATE, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY, DAY_DIMENSION.CY_YEAR_YYYY||LPAD(DAY_DIMENSION.CY_WK_OF_YEAR,2,'0')

MAPPLET.DESCRIPTION: This mapplet performs a lookup on slba_item to retrieve the item id. If the valid item id is not found for a particular line of business, the default item id is retrieved from the second lookup named LKP_SLBA_ITEM_DFLT_ITEM_ID. This mapplet has been modified to take care that all incoming fields to the transformations are trimmed before comparing.
MAPPLET.NAME: ML_ITEM_LKP_YSP3

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup fetches data from slba_item for a particular line of business as specified in the parameter file and retrieves those values which will be used for the lookup. The other values will be defaulted to '1'. Output of this lookup will be the item id.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.GARM_PER_PKG_QTY) as GARM_PER_PKG_QTY, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.ATTRIBUTION_CODE),'1') as ATTRIBUTION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.BRAND_CODE),'1') as BRAND_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.COLOR_CODE),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.COLOR_CODE),'slca',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.COLOR_CODE),'1') as COLOR_CODE, TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_CODE) as DIVISION_CODE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slu',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SKU),'sls',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SKU),'sld',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SKU),'1') as SKU, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SIZE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SIZE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.SIZE_NUM),'1') as SIZE_NUM, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slca',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.CUP_SIZE),'1') as CUP_SIZE, DECODE(LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')),'slh',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM),'slsp',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM),'slca',TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM),'1') as STYLE_NUM, TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP) as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP')) <> 'sli' AND LOWER(TRIM(SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP)) = LOWER(TRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP'))

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup condition
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: ATTRIBUTION_CODE = I_ATTRIBUTION_CODE AND BRAND_CODE = I_BRAND_CODE AND COLOR_CODE = I_COLOR_CODE AND SKU = I_SKU AND SIZE_NUM = I_SIZE_NUM AND CUP_SIZE = I_CUP_SIZE AND STYLE_NUM = I_STYLE_NUM AND DIVISION_GROUP = I_DIVISION_GROUP AND DIVISION_CODE = I_DIVISION_CODE

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, TRIM(A.COMPANY_CODE) || TRIM(A.DIVISION_CODE) || TRIM(A.STYLE_NUM) || TRIM(A.COLOR_CODE) || TRIM(A.SIZE_NUM) || TRIM(A.CUP_SIZE) as SIZE_NUM, A.DIVISION_GROUP AS DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM A LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT ITEM_ID FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='sli' and ITEM_TYPE_CODE='MFG') B ON A.ITEM_ID = B.ITEM_ID WHERE A.DIVISION_GROUP = 'sli' AND B.ITEM_ID IS NULL

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT A.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, A.COMPANY_CODE||A.DIVISION_CODE||A.UPC_CODE as UPC_CODE, A.DIVISION_GROUP AS DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM A LEFT OUTER JOIN (SELECT ITEM_ID FROM ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP='sli' and ITEM_TYPE_CODE='MFG') B ON A.ITEM_ID = B.ITEM_ID WHERE A.DIVISION_GROUP = 'sli' AND B.ITEM_ID IS NULL

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This expression generalizes the item id that is sent as output based on various conditions, being the line of business ans whether the input values for some lines of business are null.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_ITEM_ID

TRANSFORMFIELD.EXPRESSION: IIF(ISNULL(I_ITEM_ID), IIF( (I_SLBA_DIVISION_CODE = 'SC' AND ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(SKU)))) OR (I_SLBA_DIVISION_CODE = 'HS' AND ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(STYLE_NUM)))) OR (I_SLBA_DIVISION_CODE = 'CH' AND ISNULL(LTRIM(RTRIM(STYLE_NUM)))), V_DFLT_ITEM_ID,NULL ), I_ITEM_ID)
TRANSFORMFIELD.NAME: V_ITEM_ID

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: This lookup on slba_item retrieves the default item for that lin of business if the valid item id is not found.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_SLBA_ITEM_DFLT_ITEM

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT SLBA_ITEM.ITEM_ID as ITEM_ID, SLBA_ITEM.STYLE_NUM as STYLE_NUM, SLBA_ITEM.DIVISION_GROUP as DIVISION_GROUP FROM SLBA_ITEM WHERE DIVISION_GROUP = LTRIM(RTRIM('$$DIVISION_GROUP'))

TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_TSUM_C11

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT C.SKU_ID AS SKU_ID, C.EVENT_ID AS EVENT_ID, SUBSTR(C.EVENT_ID,3,2) AS EVENT_ID_SUBSTR, C.FYR_WK_ID AS FYR_WK_ID, S.ITEMS_PER_PACK AS ITEMS_PER_PACK, C.ACTL_SALE_DOL_AMT AS ACTL_SALE_DOL_AMT , C.ACTL_SALE_COS_AMT AS ACTL_SALE_COS_AMT, C.ACTL_SALE_UNIT_QTY AS ACTL_SALE_UNIT_QTY FROM PCATWH.TSUM_C11@GANYMEDE C, PCATWH.TLU_SKU@GANYMEDE K, PCATWH.TLU_STYLE@GANYMEDE S WHERE C.SKU_ID=K.SKU_ID AND K.STYLE_ID=S.STYLE_ID AND C.FYR_WK_ID=(SELECT FYR_WK_ID FROM PCATWH.TLU_CUR_WK) AND (C.ACTL_SALE_UNIT_QTY > 0 OR C.ACTL_SALE_DOL_AMT > 0 OR C.ACTL_SALE_COS_AMT > 0) AND SUBSTR(C.EVENT_ID,3,2) IN ('71','72')
